1
00:01:37,056 --> 00:01:39,475
-保罗·威沃!-是的，先生。
- Paul Weevo! - Yes, sir.

2
00:01:39,559 --> 00:01:42,103
-能听到我说话吗?-是的，阿奇先生。
- Can you hear me? - Yes, sir, Mr. Archie.

3
00:01:42,186 --> 00:01:44,564
-你能找到洞吗?-是的，先生，很多。
- Can you find the holes? - Yes, sir. Lots of them.

4
00:01:44,647 --> 00:01:46,149
那你一定要买大的。
Well, make sure you get the big ones.

5
00:01:46,232 --> 00:01:47,859
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

6
00:01:58,244 --> 00:01:59,930
愉快大叔，你没事做吗?
Uncle Pleasant, ain't you got nothing to do?

7
00:01:59,954 --> 00:02:01,497
什么都没有。
Not a thing.

8
00:02:04,125 --> 00:02:06,878
-你不打算帮他吗?-我退休了。
- Ain't you going to help him? - I'm retired.

9
00:02:16,512 --> 00:02:18,139
娃娃。
Baby Doll.

10
00:03:07,814 --> 00:03:09,774
嘘嘘嘘。
Shh, shh, shh, shh.

11
00:03:49,981 --> 00:03:52,567
阿奇·李，你真是一团糟。
Archie Lee, you're a mess.

12
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:54,569
你知道他们怎么称呼这种人吗?
Do you know what they call such people?

13
00:03:54,652 --> 00:03:56,612
偷窥!
Peeping Toms!

14
00:03:56,696 --> 00:03:59,198
这是我的房子!
This is my house!

15
00:03:59,282 --> 00:04:03,661
难道没有一个女人是为了远离丈夫而睡在婴儿床上的吗?
And there's no name for a woman that sleeps in a baby's crib to stay away from her husband?

16
00:04:03,745 --> 00:04:06,247
现在我要用口香糖把墙上的洞堵上。
Now I'm gonna plug up the hole in that wall with chewing gum.

17
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:12,462
如果我哪天抓到你捅…再捅一刀在我睡梦中偷窥我，我要搬进棉花王酒店。
And if I ever catch you pokin' a... a knife through it again to peek at me in my sleep, I'm movin' into the Cotton King Hotel.

18
00:04:12,545 --> 00:04:17,800
你能不能，别让你那些肮脏的老狗碰我的家具?
And would you, please, keep your filthy old dogs off my furniture?

19
00:04:17,884 --> 00:04:19,886
让我和你谈谈。
Let me talk with you.

20
00:04:19,969 --> 00:04:22,180
-听着，我想要…-省省吧。
- Now, listen, I wanna have... - Spare your breath.

21
00:04:22,263 --> 00:04:25,808
留着给你那破轧棉机招揽生意吧。
Save it to drum up some business for your broken-down cotton gin.

22
00:04:25,892 --> 00:04:28,060
把门关上，我好穿衣服。
And close that door so I can get into my clothes.

23
00:04:28,144 --> 00:04:32,565
去吧，穿上你的衣服……除非你到那扇门的另一边把我们之间的门关上。
Go on, just get into your clothes... Not till you get on the other side of that door and close it between us.

24
00:04:32,648 --> 00:04:38,112
今天是11月5日，明天是11月6日，再后天是11月7日。
Today is the fifth day of November, tomorrow's the sixth day of November, and the day after that is November 7.

25
00:04:38,196 --> 00:04:40,907
你知道那是什么日子吧?
And you know what day that is, don't you?

26
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:43,785
11月7日是你20岁生日。
November 7 is your 20th birthday.

27
00:04:43,868 --> 00:04:46,871
你还记得真是太好了?
Ain't that sweet of you to remember?

28
00:04:46,954 --> 00:04:48,706
我的生日礼物呢?
Where's my birthday present?

29
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:51,584
哦，你会收到生日礼物的。
Oh, you'll get your birthday present.

30
00:04:51,667 --> 00:04:57,173
如果你没有忘记我们之间的协议，那将在那天到期。
Providing you haven't forgotten the agreement between us, which comes due on that day.

31
00:04:59,133 --> 00:05:00,593
哦，协议?
Oh, the agreement?

32
00:05:00,676 --> 00:05:02,386
是啊，协议。
Yeah, uh-huh, the agreement.

33
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:04,764
你对着《圣经》发誓要守住这一方。
Which you swore on a Bible to keep your side of.

34
00:05:04,847 --> 00:05:06,349
只要你能保住你的。
Providin' you kept yours.

35
00:05:06,432 --> 00:05:16,984
我有没有碰过你，自从我们…是啊，越频繁越好，还被扇了耳光…有我吗?有我吗?我曾经，曾经，曾经强迫过你成为你的丈夫吗?
Have I ever laid hands on you since we've been... Yeah, as often as possible and gotten slapped off... Have I? Have I? Have I ever, ever, ever once forced myself on you as your husband by law?

36
00:05:17,068 --> 00:05:19,237
难道律法对你毫无意义吗?
Or don't the law mean nothing to you?

37
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,489
你那边的协议呢?
How about your side of the agreement?

38
00:05:21,572 --> 00:05:25,493
你追求我的时候，说得太大了，大人物。
You talked big, mighty big when you was courting me, bigshot.

39
00:05:25,576 --> 00:05:29,413
你跟我爸说要把我安置在全县最豪华的房子里。
You told my daddy you was gonna put me in the grandest house in the county.

40
00:05:29,497 --> 00:05:32,875
我把你放在虎尾监狱了。是我买的，我把你放在里面。
Well, I put you in Tiger Tail. I bought it and I put you in it.

41
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:35,503
虎尾是全县最宏伟的房子。
And Tiger Tail is the grandest house in the county.

42
00:05:35,586 --> 00:05:39,549
是啊，你让我去了虎尾监狱，整个三角洲最大的破地方。
Yeah, you put me in Tiger Tail, the biggest old wreck of a place in the whole delta.

43
00:05:39,632 --> 00:05:44,971
你跟我爸说你要把这地方恢复到多宾家以前的样子，只会更好。
You told my daddy you was gonna restore this place exactly like it was when the Dobines owned it, only better.

44
00:05:45,054 --> 00:05:48,891
“做个展示的地方，”你说。是啊，怪胎秀。
"Make a show place," you said. Yeah, a freak show.

45
00:05:48,975 --> 00:05:50,415
屋顶上有个男孩。
I've got a boy on the roof right now.

46
00:05:50,476 --> 00:05:52,436
我的人已经在屋顶上了。
I've got my man on the roof now.

47
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,705
你没听到锤子敲屋顶的声音吗?
Can't you hear the hammer on the roof?

48
00:05:53,729 --> 00:05:56,983
那是锤子吗?我还以为那是特大白蚁呢。
Is that a hammer? Why, I thought that was a king-size termite.

49
00:05:57,066 --> 00:06:03,447
混蛋，如果你不是最忘恩负义的小…我已经抵押了自己来满足你的要求。
Doggone, if you ain't the most ungrateful little... I have mortgaged myself to satisfy your demands.

50
00:06:03,531 --> 00:06:07,952
为了得到我，你对我爸爸撒了一大堆谎。
You told a mouthful of lies to my daddy in order to get me.

51
00:06:08,035 --> 00:06:11,455
得到你吗?我还没抓到你。
Get you? I ain't got you yet.

52
00:06:11,539 --> 00:06:13,749
哦，你也不会这么做的。
Oh, and you ain't about to either.

53
00:06:13,833 --> 00:06:22,216
现在我告诉你，如果理想即走即付家具公司把这五套完整的家具从这所房子里搬走，那么这个协议
Now I'm telling you that if the Ideal Pay As You Go Plan Furniture Company removes those five complete sets of furniture from this house, then that agreement

54
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:25,052
你刚才说的自动取消了。
you just spoke about is automatically cancelled.

55
00:06:25,136 --> 00:06:29,515
现在你能回自己房间去吗?
And now would you kindly go back in your own room?

56
00:06:29,599 --> 00:06:33,769
我今天在城里的时候要找份薪水不错的工作。
I'm gonna get me a good-payin' job while I'm in town today.

57
00:06:33,853 --> 00:06:37,189
只是以防万一。只是以防万一。
Just in case. Just in case.

58
00:06:48,701 --> 00:06:51,162
对着镜子欣赏自己。
Admirin' yourself in the mirror.

59
00:06:51,245 --> 00:06:53,289
你看看你自己。
You just look at yourself.

60
00:06:53,372 --> 00:06:57,793
阿奇·李·梅根，你可不是一个年轻女孩的梦想成真。
You're not exactly a young girl's dream come true, Archie Lee Meighan.

61
00:06:57,877 --> 00:07:00,838
有一个叫乌鸦奶奶的老女巫。
There was an old witch named Granny Crow.

62
00:07:00,922 --> 00:07:03,883
她吐的地方，寸草不生。
Wherever she spit, no grass would grow.

63
00:07:06,135 --> 00:07:11,182
阿奇·李，那个老巫婆肯定吐在你头上了。
That old witch must have spit right on the top of your head, Archie Lee.

64
00:07:13,893 --> 00:07:16,187
谢谢，谢谢。
Thank you, thank you.

65
00:07:18,064 --> 00:07:23,110
你不是女人。你是个未成熟的女人，所以我会体谅你的。
You're not a woman. You're a woman not grown, therefore I'll make allowances.

66
00:07:26,113 --> 00:07:28,699
每次电话一响，萝丝·康弗姨妈就尖叫。
Aunt Rose Comfort screams every time that phone rings.

67
00:07:28,783 --> 00:07:31,535
哦，她为什么要做那样的蠢事?
Oh, why does she do a fool thing like that for?

68
00:07:31,619 --> 00:07:33,412
她说电话铃声让她害怕。
She says phone ringing scares her.

69
00:07:33,496 --> 00:07:36,499
萝丝阿姨，你为什么不接电话?
Aunt Rose, why don't you answer the phone?

70
00:07:40,378 --> 00:07:43,714
-萝丝阿姨!-我发誓。
- Aunt Rose! - My word.

71
00:07:43,798 --> 00:07:46,050
阿姨玫瑰!
Aunt Rose!

72
00:07:48,094 --> 00:07:51,013
玫瑰阿姨安慰!
Aunt Rose Comfort!

73
00:07:51,097 --> 00:07:53,766
萝丝阿姨康弗，你为什么不回答?
Aunt Rose Comfort, why don't you answer?

74
00:07:53,849 --> 00:07:55,476
我喘不上气了，阿奇·李。
I can't catch my breath, Archie Lee.

75
00:07:55,559 --> 00:07:57,478
电话把我吓了一跳。
Phone give me such a fright.

76
00:07:57,561 --> 00:08:00,690
回答这个问题!
Answer it!

77
00:08:00,773 --> 00:08:04,360
喂?我是罗斯·康弗·麦考克尔小姐。
Hello? This is Miss Rose Comfort McCorkle speaking.

78
00:08:04,443 --> 00:08:12,010
不，房子的女主人是阿奇·李·梅根太太，我过世哥哥的女儿……现在他们不想知道了。现在是谁在说话?
No, the lady of the house is Mrs. Archie Lee Meighan, daughter of my brother who passed away... Now they don't wanna know that. Now who is it talking?

79
00:08:12,034 --> 00:08:14,453
-他们想要什么?-我听不太清楚。
- And what do they want? - I don't hear very well.

80
00:08:14,537 --> 00:08:18,040
请你说大声一点好吗?
Would you, please, speak a little louder?

81
00:08:18,124 --> 00:08:21,794
哦，理想的即走即付计划?
Oh, the Ideal Pay As You Go Plan?

82
00:08:21,877 --> 00:08:25,089
-是的…-把电话给我。
- Yeah... - Give me that phone.

83
00:08:25,172 --> 00:08:27,633
这是什么，孩子?
Now what is this, boy?

84
00:08:27,717 --> 00:08:30,052
是的。今天好吗?
Yeah. Today?

85
00:08:30,136 --> 00:08:33,597
不，你得再给我点时间。
Oh, no, you've got to give me a little more time.

86
00:08:33,681 --> 00:08:41,230
嗯，你知道，我最近在生意上遇到了一点挫折……辛迪加种植园建立了他们自己的轧棉机我失去了他们的生意。
Well, you see, I've had a little setback in business lately... Well, the Syndicate Plantation built their own cotton gin and I've lost their trade.

87
00:08:41,313 --> 00:08:44,942
我还需要点时间才能恢复过来。
Well, it's gonna take me a little more time to recover from that.

88
00:08:46,527 --> 00:08:48,529
那就把它拿出来!
Then take it out!

89
00:08:48,612 --> 00:08:51,032
把它拿出来，拿出来，拿出来!
Take it out, out, out!

90
00:08:51,115 --> 00:08:53,826
你再也别想要我的生意了。不,决不!
You'll never get my business again. No, never!

91
00:09:01,709 --> 00:09:07,506
阿奇·李，亲爱的，你们不会失去你们的罚款…你能闭嘴，回厨房去吗?
Oh, Archie Lee honey, you all aren't gonna lose your fine... Would you shut up and get on back in that kitchen?

92
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:11,343
还有，你在电话里听到的话，一个字也别跟我妻子说，如果你听到一个字的话。
And don't you speak a word that you heard on this phone, if you heard a word, to my wife.

93
00:09:11,427 --> 00:09:13,429
别再在这屋里嚷嚷了。
Don't holler no more in this house.

94
00:09:13,512 --> 00:09:15,973
别再咯咯笑了。
Don't cackle no more.

95
00:09:16,057 --> 00:09:21,479
我保证，我会帮你收拾行李的。我会帮你收拾行李，把你送到日落街的乡下家。
I guarantee, I'll pack you up. I'll pack you up and haul you off to that county home at Sunset.

96
00:09:21,562 --> 00:09:22,980
你说什么，阿奇·李?
What did you say, Archie Lee?

97
00:09:23,064 --> 00:09:24,690
你对我说什么了吗，阿奇·李?
You say something to me, Archie Lee?

98
00:09:24,774 --> 00:09:26,400
是的。
Yeah.

99
00:09:26,484 --> 00:09:29,904
-我说射击!——哦。
- I said shoot! - Oh.

100
00:09:36,577 --> 00:09:38,496
这次是什么让她大叫?
What made her holler this time?

101
00:09:38,579 --> 00:09:43,542
我怎么知道是什么让那个老妇人这一次，最后一次，或者下次大叫?
How do I know what made that old woman holler this time or last time or the next time she hollers?

102
00:09:43,626 --> 00:09:47,046
她上次大吼大叫是因为你朝她扔了东西。
Last time she hollered was 'cause you throwed somethin' at her.

103
00:09:47,129 --> 00:09:49,131
我扔给萝丝阿姨什么安慰?
What did I ever throw at Aunt Rose Comfort?

104
00:09:49,215 --> 00:09:52,968
一杯水，在厨房里唱教堂赞美诗。
A glass of water and for singing church hymns in the kitchen.

105
00:09:53,052 --> 00:09:55,846
水吗?为什么，这么多水。
Water? Why, this much water.

106
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:57,765
我几乎没洒在她身上。
I barely sprinkled her with it.

107
00:09:57,848 --> 00:10:00,476
-她什么都没听到。-我知道。
- She don't hear nothing. - I know.

108
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:04,039
-你…-你总得做点什么来引起那个老太太的注意，不是吗?
- Well, you... - Well, you gotta do something to get the old woman's attention, don't you?

109
00:10:04,063 --> 00:10:06,190
是的。嗯?
Yeah. Huh?

110
00:10:06,273 --> 00:10:14,073
-嘿，嘿，放我下来。-拿上你的…让你的…让你的…-把手拿开!——哦!
- Hey, hey, put me down. - Get your... Get your... get your... - Get your hands off me! - Oh!

111
00:10:14,156 --> 00:10:16,075
-脱下来!——哦!
- Take them off! - Oh!

112
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:30,881
我…我…下次你再违背我们的协议我就搬去棉花王酒店，就下次。
I'm... I'm... I'm moving to the Cotton King Hotel the very next time you try to break our agreement, the very next time.

113
00:10:41,892 --> 00:10:43,727
娃娃!
Baby Doll!

114
00:10:48,607 --> 00:10:50,317
娃娃!
Baby Doll!

115
00:10:57,449 --> 00:10:59,803
哦，如果你要和我一起进城，你就过来吧。
Oh, you come on down here if you're going into town with me.

116
00:10:59,827 --> 00:11:02,204
我十分钟前就得去看医生了。
I gotta be at the doctor's ten minutes ago.

117
00:11:18,262 --> 00:11:21,515
娃娃!
Baby Doll!

118
00:11:21,599 --> 00:11:24,268
如果你这么没耐心，就先走吧。
If you're so impatient, just go ahead without me.

119
00:11:24,351 --> 00:11:28,606
去吧!不用你，我也有很多办法去市中心。
Just go ahead! I've got plenty of ways of getting downtown without you.

120
00:11:28,689 --> 00:11:31,609
这是事实。
That's the truth.

121
00:11:35,905 --> 00:11:38,073
你来吧!
You come on!

122
00:11:52,171 --> 00:11:54,590
你把你的棉花尾巴拿下来。
You get your cotton-picking tail down here.

123
00:12:05,935 --> 00:12:07,895
慢慢来。
Take your time.

124
00:12:13,901 --> 00:12:15,903
-早上好，山姆。——女士。
- Morning, Sam. - Ma'am.

125
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:24,119
那你还在等什么?
Well, what are you waiting for?

126
00:12:24,203 --> 00:12:27,623
来吧，上车吧。
Oh, now come on, get into the car.

127
00:12:27,706 --> 00:12:34,838
我会坐到那艘散船的后座等你下车，像个绅士一样给我开门。
I will get into the backseat of that scatter boat when you get out and walk around and open the door for me like a gentleman.

128
00:12:34,922 --> 00:12:38,592
如果你是在等这个，那你得等很长时间了。
Well, you're gonna wait a long time if that's what you're waiting for.

129
00:12:38,676 --> 00:12:42,263
好吧，我敢说，我父亲会在坟墓里翻来覆去。
Well, I declare, my father would turn over in his grave.

130
00:12:42,346 --> 00:12:47,559
我从未见过你父亲下车为任何女人打开车门尤其是你那摇摇晃晃的母亲。
I never once saw your father get out and open the car door for any woman and especially not your waddle-legged mother.

131
00:12:47,643 --> 00:12:49,478
现在上车吧!
Now get on in!

132
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:10,708
嘿,Sid !来这里!
Hey, Sid! Come here!

133
00:13:10,791 --> 00:13:12,501
-嘿，希德，过来——啊。
- Hey, Sid, come here. - Ughh.

134
00:13:12,584 --> 00:13:15,504
-我们为什么要停在这里?-你在这里做什么?
- What are we stoppin' here for? - What are you doing here?

135
00:13:15,587 --> 00:13:17,965
瓦卡罗现在让我为他工作了。
Well, Vacarro's got me working for him now.

136
00:13:18,048 --> 00:13:20,175
为他吗?你为他工作?
For him? You're working for him?

137
00:13:20,259 --> 00:13:23,220
我还能做什么?辛迪加把我的杜松子酒关了。
What else could I do? Syndicate shut my gin down tight.

138
00:13:23,304 --> 00:13:25,264
-怎么回事?-哦，这是个派对。
- What's going on? - Oh, it's a party.

139
00:13:25,347 --> 00:13:26,724
某种庆祝活动。
A celebration of some kind.

140
00:13:26,807 --> 00:13:28,976
辛迪加为什么不庆祝?
Why shouldn't the Syndicate celebrate?

141
00:13:29,059 --> 00:13:32,354
这里的生意在全县都有。
It's got every last bit of business in the county.

142
00:13:32,438 --> 00:13:36,066
包括我过去得到的每一点和你过去得到的每一点。
