In just three hours, three hours, the terms of our agreement will be settled for good.

1041
01:25:37,550 --> 01:25:39,802
-别指望了。-午夜时分。
- Don't count on it. - Sharp at midnight.

1042
01:25:39,886 --> 01:25:41,196
最近这里发生的事太多了。
Too much has happened here lately.

1043
01:25:41,220 --> 01:25:43,681
我的信用卡又大开了。
Well, my credit is wide open again.

1044
01:25:43,765 --> 01:25:46,309
如果真相大白，监狱的大门也会关上。
And so is the jailhouse door if the truth comes out.

1045
01:25:46,392 --> 01:25:52,231
你是在用黑色威胁我吗?嗨!,席尔瓦!
Are you threatenin' me with black... Heigh-ho, Silva!

1046
01:25:55,068 --> 01:26:03,034
阿奇·李，瓦卡罗先生说他可能不会买一台新的轧棉机但可能会让你一直为他轧棉。
Archie Lee, Mr. Vacarro says that he might not put up a new cotton gin but might let you gin out his cotton for him all the time.

1047
01:26:03,117 --> 01:26:05,244
你不高兴吗?
Ain't you pleased about that?

1048
01:26:05,328 --> 01:26:08,206
他明天会带更多的棉花来。
He's gonna come tomorrow with lots more cotton.

1049
01:26:08,289 --> 01:26:12,043
在你发泄的时候，他会让我招待他。
And while you're ginnin' it out, he's gonna have me entertain him.

1050
01:26:12,126 --> 01:26:14,587
给他做柠檬水。
Make lemonade for him.

1051
01:26:14,671 --> 01:26:17,715
而且还会没完没了。甚至可能到明年秋天。
And it's gonna go on and on. Maybe even till next fall.

1052
01:26:20,677 --> 01:26:23,304
这是实际的睦邻政策。
It's the good neighbor policy in practice.

1053
01:26:23,388 --> 01:26:25,807
哦!
Oh!

1054
01:26:32,313 --> 01:26:34,190
你在这里多久了?
How long you been on the place?

1055
01:26:34,273 --> 01:26:38,861
整个漫长的秋天下午，都是我自找的。
All this unusually long fall afternoon, I've imposed on your hospitality.

1056
01:26:44,701 --> 01:26:46,202
你来过哪里?
Where you been here?

1057
01:26:46,285 --> 01:26:49,455
在你唯一剩下的床上打个盹。
Taking a nap on your only remainin' bed.

1058
01:26:49,539 --> 01:26:53,042
育婴室里放下板条的婴儿床。
The crib in the nursery with the slats let down.

1059
01:26:53,126 --> 01:26:55,628
有些悲伤，懂我的意思吗?
Something sad about it, know what I mean?

1060
01:26:55,712 --> 01:26:57,255
伤心什么?
Sad about what?

1061
01:26:57,338 --> 01:27:02,552
空房:房子里没有人住的育婴室，其他房间都是空的
An unoccupied nursery in a house and all the other rooms empty.

1062
01:27:04,762 --> 01:27:06,681
那不关你的事。
That's no problem of yours.

1063
01:27:06,764 --> 01:27:11,185
睦邻政策使你的问题成为我的问题，反之亦然。
The good neighbor policy makes your problems mine and vice-versa.

1064
01:27:11,269 --> 01:27:13,020
晚饭准备好了，孩子们。
Supper ready, children.

1065
01:27:13,104 --> 01:27:16,232
你们没听见我们被叫去吃晚饭吗?
Well, didn't you all hear us called in to supper?

1066
01:27:19,694 --> 01:27:21,571
你今晚要在这里吃吗?
You're gonna eat here tonight?

1067
01:27:21,654 --> 01:27:24,365
梅根太太让我留下来吃晚饭。
Oh, Mrs. Meighan asked me to stay for supper.

1068
01:27:24,449 --> 01:27:31,789
但我告诉她，在我接受邀请之前，我最好先听听户主的邀请。
But I told her I better get to hear the invitation from the head of the house before I'd feel free to accept it.

1069
01:27:31,873 --> 01:27:34,000
你怎么看?
So what do you say?

1070
01:27:38,504 --> 01:27:40,840
留下来吃晚饭。
Stay for supper.

1071
01:27:40,923 --> 01:27:43,676
好吧，你只能碰碰运气了。
Well, you'll have to take pot luck.

1072
01:27:43,760 --> 01:27:45,928
我不会打扰你吧?
I wouldn't be putting you out?

1073
01:27:47,930 --> 01:27:52,185
哦。不好意思，我得去换衣服了。
Oh. Excuse me, I better get into my clothes.

1074
01:27:52,268 --> 01:27:54,812
是啊，你最好这样。
Oh, yeah, you better.

1075
01:28:40,441 --> 01:28:50,284
我明白你的意思了吗?,嗯…你不愿意造一个新的杜松子酒却把你的生意留给我?
Did I understand you to say that... that, uh... you wouldn't build a new gin but would leave your business to me?

1076
01:28:50,368 --> 01:28:53,037
-如果你同意的话…-我不知道。
- If that's agreeable with you... - I don't know about that.

1077
01:28:56,666 --> 01:28:59,544
嗯，我得考虑一下这件事。
Well, I've got to consider the matter.

1078
01:28:59,627 --> 01:29:10,346
涉及到资金，比如新设备和……和…我们现在进去吃饭吧。
Financing is involved, such as new equipment and... and... Let's go in and eat now.

1079
01:29:10,429 --> 01:29:15,393
我肚子疼。我得到了……我有点…胃灼热。
I got a pain in the belly. I got... I got a sort of... heartburn.

1080
01:29:19,772 --> 01:29:21,566
嘿。
Hey.

1081
01:29:21,649 --> 01:29:25,111
嘿!又多了一个席位。
Hey! One more place at the table.

1082
01:29:25,194 --> 01:29:28,197
辛迪加种植园的瓦卡罗先生留下来吃晚饭。
Mr. Vacarro from the Syndicate Plantation is staying for supper.

1083
01:29:28,281 --> 01:29:30,867
我不知道会有人来。
I had no idea company was expected.

1084
01:29:30,950 --> 01:29:35,204
现在让我换衣服……另一个地方就够了。
Now just let me change... Another place is all that's called for.

1085
01:29:40,376 --> 01:29:42,169
你一整天都在这里吗?——嗯?
- Have you been here all day? - Huh?

1086
01:29:42,253 --> 01:29:46,358
你整个下午都在家还是去县医院吃巧克力糖了?
Have you been in the house all afternoon or did you ride out to the county hospital to eat some more chocolate candy?

1087
01:29:46,382 --> 01:29:48,843
是的，我去医院看望了一位朋友。
Yes, I visited a friend in the hospital.

1088
01:29:48,926 --> 01:29:53,973
然后你出去了，而我…我拼命地工作!
Then you were out while I... I worked like the hammers of hell!

1089
01:29:54,056 --> 01:29:59,812
我回到家，发现阁楼的地板塌下来了，我妻子脾气暴躁，还在侮辱人，晚餐是猪粪!
I come home to find the attic floor has fell through, my wife bad-tempered and insultin', and a supper of hog slops!

1090
01:29:59,896 --> 01:30:02,023
我想你有……
I suppose you've got...

1091
01:30:04,901 --> 01:30:07,862
坐下来。我得打个电话。
Sit down. I've gotta make me a phone call.

1092
01:30:16,245 --> 01:30:18,623
你好。我要"亮点"霍普金斯小姐。
Hello. I want the Bright Spot, Miss Hopkins.

1093
01:30:18,706 --> 01:30:20,625
把亮点给我。
Give me the Bright Spot.

1094
01:30:20,708 --> 01:30:23,210
我想不起数字了。现在给我，听到了吗?
I can't think of the number. Now you give it to me, you hear?

1095
01:30:29,008 --> 01:30:30,551
你好，亮点?
Hello, Bright Spot?

1096
01:30:33,471 --> 01:30:34,805
他在打电话。
He's on the phone about somethin'.

1097
01:30:34,889 --> 01:30:40,186
如果我是你，我就不会闲逛……我口袋里有张黑桃a我也要让他在上面签名。
If I was you, I wouldn't hang around... I've got the ace of spades in my pocket and I'm gonna get his autograph on it too.

1098
01:30:40,269 --> 01:30:41,812
哦，别指望法庭的法律。
Oh, don't count on the law of court.

1099
01:30:41,896 --> 01:30:43,816
这里的正义就像那个老妇人一样又聋又瞎。
Justice here is deaf and blind as that old woman.

1100
01:30:43,856 --> 01:30:45,942
我做我自己的事。
I do my own justice.

1101
01:30:46,025 --> 01:30:51,238
叫艾迪，比尔，布茨，罗兹，他们中的任何一个。
Get Eddie, Bill, Boots, Rhodes, anyone of them.

1102
01:30:51,322 --> 01:30:53,950
我建议你，趁他还在打电话，赶紧走。
I'm advising you, go while he's on the phone.

1103
01:30:54,033 --> 01:30:56,911
你不了解他的朋友。他们……他们是可怕的。
You don't know his friends. They're... they're awful.

1104
01:30:56,994 --> 01:30:58,537
我见过他们。
I've seen them.

1105
01:31:00,289 --> 01:31:02,959
我发现你今晚有些不一样。
I find you different this evenin' in some way.

1106
01:31:05,086 --> 01:31:06,921
没关系。
Never mind that.

1107
01:31:07,004 --> 01:31:08,923
趁他还在打电话，快走吧。
Just go while he's still on the phone.

1108
01:31:09,006 --> 01:31:10,925
突然长大了。
Grown up suddenly.

1109
01:31:16,430 --> 01:31:19,892
我平生第一次感到凉爽和放松。
I feel cool and rested for the first time in my life.

1110
01:31:21,811 --> 01:31:24,522
这就是我的感受。
That's the way I feel.

1111
01:31:24,605 --> 01:31:27,316
休息好了，凉快了。
Rested and cool.

1112
01:31:27,400 --> 01:31:30,695
现在他在这个县无处可逃了。
Now there's no place he can run to in this county.

1113
01:31:30,778 --> 01:31:34,490
嗯。你说得对，孩子。
Hmm. Well, you can say that again, boy.

1114
01:31:34,573 --> 01:31:37,576
是的。嗯哼。
Yeah. Mm-hmm.

1115
01:32:02,560 --> 01:32:05,563
如果你不能离开，那就派人来。
If you can't leave the place, then you send someone.

1116
01:32:05,646 --> 01:32:08,024
但你派人去找他，听到了吗?
But you send someone to find him, you hear me?

1117
01:32:10,818 --> 01:32:13,070
我再打给你。
I'll call you back.

1118
01:32:13,154 --> 01:32:16,449
自然之诗。如果我有……不要在意大自然的诗。
Poems of nature. If I had... Never mind the poems of nature.

1119
01:32:16,532 --> 01:32:18,451
再见。我一会儿打给你。
Goodbye. I'll call you later.

1120
01:32:20,202 --> 01:32:22,747
早知道有人陪我就好了。
If I'd only known company was expected.

1121
01:32:22,830 --> 01:32:24,683
-把食物放在桌子上。-稍等一下。
- Put some food on the table. - Just take a minute.

1122
01:32:24,707 --> 01:32:26,876
我们不会再等了。
We ain't gonna wait no minute.

1123
01:32:30,921 --> 01:32:33,049
拿些吃的出来!
Bring out some food!

1124
01:32:50,900 --> 01:32:56,363
这就是他们所说的…你这是蒙娜丽莎式的微笑吗，小猫咪?
Is that what they call a... a Mona Lisa smile you got on you, puss?

1125
01:32:58,991 --> 01:33:01,160
把食物放在桌子上!
Put some food on the table!

1126
01:33:01,243 --> 01:33:03,913
别挑玫瑰阿姨的毛病。
Don't pick on Aunt Rose Comfort.

1127
01:33:03,996 --> 01:33:06,707
今晚我要和那个老太太好好谈谈。
I'm gonna have a talk with that old woman right here tonight.

1128
01:33:06,791 --> 01:33:08,834
她待得太久了。
She's outstayed her welcome.

1129
01:33:12,463 --> 01:33:15,633
你今晚戴的蓝丝带真漂亮，梅根太太。
What a pretty blue ribbon you're wearing tonight, Mrs. Meighan.

1130
01:33:17,343 --> 01:33:19,386
谢谢你，瓦卡罗先生。
Why, thank you, Mr. Vacarro.

1131
01:33:19,470 --> 01:33:22,848
蓝色有那么多深浅。
There's so many shades of blue.

1132
01:33:22,932 --> 01:33:25,101
那是什么颜色?
What particular shade is that?

1133
01:33:25,184 --> 01:33:27,103
它是浅蓝色的。
It's just baby blue.

1134
01:33:29,271 --> 01:33:31,482
衬托出你蓝色的眼睛。
Brings out the blue of your eyes.

1135
01:33:31,565 --> 01:33:33,609
食物!
Food!

1136
01:33:33,692 --> 01:33:36,779
——食品!-马上，马上。
- Food! - Immediately, this instant.

1137
01:33:39,990 --> 01:33:42,576
这件毛衣是我嫁妆的一部分。
This sweater was part of my trousseau.

1138
01:33:42,660 --> 01:33:48,666
我所有的嫁妆都是在我爸爸出名的孟菲斯的百货公司买的。
I got all my trousseau at various department stores in Memphis where my daddy was known.

1139
01:33:48,749 --> 01:33:52,002
-这是什么东西?草?-是绿色的。
- What is this stuff? Grass? - It's greens.

1140
01:33:52,086 --> 01:33:53,963
难道你看不出绿色吗?
Don't you know greens when you see them?

1141
01:33:54,046 --> 01:33:59,009
主街上的大百货商店……这东西是绿色的吗?
Big department stores on Main Street... This stuff is greens?

1142
01:33:59,093 --> 01:34:01,095
阿奇·李特别喜欢吃绿色蔬菜。
Archie Lee dotes on greens.

1143
01:34:01,178 --> 01:34:03,264
-是吗，阿奇·李?-不，我没有。
- Don't you, Archie Lee? - No, I don't.

1144
01:34:03,347 --> 01:34:06,433
你不?你不喜欢吃绿色蔬菜?
You don't? You don't dote on greens?

1145
01:34:06,517 --> 01:34:07,726
好吧，有人这么做了。
Well, somebody did.

1146
01:34:07,810 --> 01:34:12,231
也许有人在某个时候，某个地方干过，但那不代表是我干的。
Somebody probably did sometime, somewhere, but that don't mean it was me.

1147
01:34:12,314 --> 01:34:16,402
吃你的绿色蔬菜，大人物。绿色植物能增加血液中的铁元素。
Eat your greens, bigshot. Greens put iron in the blood.

1148
01:34:16,485 --> 01:34:18,320
我以为阿奇·李很喜欢吃蔬菜。
I thought Archie Lee doted on greens.

1149
01:34:18,404 --> 01:34:24,118
所有这些好恶很难在你的脑海中保持清晰，但阿奇·李(Archie Lee)很容易做饭。
All these likes and dislikes are hard to keep straight in your head, but Archie Lee is easy to cook for.

1150
01:34:24,201 --> 01:34:26,912
把桌子上的泔水拿掉。
Take this slop off the table.

1151
01:34:26,996 --> 01:34:29,832
我在伯明翰给你煮些鸡蛋。
I'll cook you some eggs Birmingham.

1152
01:34:29,915 --> 01:34:31,834
这些蔬菜没煮熟。
These greens didn't cook enough.

1153
01:34:31,917 --> 01:34:34,086
我对我的炉子开了个愚蠢的玩笑。
I played a fool trick with my stove.

1154
01:34:34,170 --> 01:34:36,589
我…我忘了点灯了。
I... I forgot to light it.

1155
01:34:39,175 --> 01:34:42,011
当我去商店的时候，我把绿色蔬菜留在炉子上了。
When I went out to the store, I left my greens on the stove.

1156
01:34:42,094 --> 01:34:43,762
我以为他们在沸腾。
I thought they were boilin'.

1157
01:34:43,846 --> 01:34:46,557
当我回到家时，我发现我的炉子还没点上。
When I came home, I discovered my stove wasn't lit.

1158
01:34:47,933 --> 01:34:49,310
你为什么说我的炉子?
Why do you say my stove?

1159
01:34:49,393 --> 01:34:53,314
为什么一切都是我的，我的，我的……阿奇·李，我想你喝多了。
Why is everything mine, mine, mine... Archie Lee, I think you've been drinkin'.

1160
01:34:53,397 --> 01:34:55,858
你别插手。坐下，罗斯阿姨。
You stay out of this. Sit down, Aunt Rose.

1161
01:34:58,360 --> 01:35:01,864
-那是什么，阿奇·李?-坐下。
- What was that, Archie Lee? - Sit down.

1162
01:35:01,947 --> 01:35:03,490
在哪里?
Where?

1163
01:35:08,787 --> 01:35:10,164
坐下来。
Sit down.

1164
01:35:18,255 --> 01:35:20,257
我要问你一个问题。
I'm gonna ask you a question.

1165
01:35:23,552 --> 01:35:26,430
你有什么计划?
What sort of plans have you made?

1166
01:35:26,513 --> 01:35:29,266
什么计划，阿奇·李?你指的是什么样的计划?
What plans, Archie Lee? What sort of plans do you mean?

1167
01:35:29,350 --> 01:35:30,726
对未来的计划。
Plans for the future.

1168
01:35:30,809 --> 01:35:34,772
阿奇·李，我觉得没必要在众人面前讨论这个问题。
Archie Lee, I don't think this discussion is necessary in front of company.

1169
01:35:34,855 --> 01:35:45,324
梅根太太，当一个人对某件事感到不舒服时，他通常会把他的烦恼发泄在一些完全无辜的人身上。
Mrs. Meighan, when someone feels uncomfortable over somethin', it often happens he takes out his annoyance on some completely innocent person.

1170
01:35:57,211 --> 01:36:00,673
露丝阿姨，你八月就来了。
Now, Aunt Rose, you've been here since August.

1171
01:36:00,756 --> 01:36:02,758
那可真够久的。
That's a mighty long stay.

1172
01:36:06,553 --> 01:36:10,099
老实说，我认为你需要休息一下。
And it's my honest opinion that you're in need of a rest.

1173
01:36:10,182 --> 01:36:14,645
你在这里和那里都做了多久了?
You've been cooking around here and cooking around there for how long now?

1174
01:36:16,313 --> 01:36:17,731
好吗?
Well?

1175
01:36:17,815 --> 01:36:21,694
你在别人家做饭有多久了?
How long you been cooking around people's houses?

1176
01:36:21,777 --> 01:36:27,449
我帮助我的亲戚，我的家人，只要他们需要我。
I helped out my relatives, my folks, whenever they needed me.

1177
01:36:27,533 --> 01:36:32,079
我总是受到邀请，有时还乞求我来。
I was always invited, sometimes begged to come.

1178
01:36:32,162 --> 01:36:37,876
当有孩子或有人生病时，他们就叫罗丝阿姨，而罗丝阿姨总是准备好了。
When babies was expected or somebody was sick, they called for Aunt Rose and Aunt Rose was always ready.

1179
01:36:39,670 --> 01:36:42,840
从来没人逼我出去。
Nobody ever had to put me out.

1180
01:36:46,093 --> 01:36:49,096
先生们，我离开餐桌好吗?我…
Will you gentlemen excuse me from the dinner table? I...

1181
01:36:51,807 --> 01:36:53,976
我去收拾行李。
I'll run up and pack.

1182
01:36:59,606 --> 01:37:01,734
罗丝小姐，等等。
Miss Rose Comfort, wait.

1183
01:37:04,903 --> 01:37:06,697
我开车送你回家。
I'll drive you home.

1184
01:37:06,780 --> 01:37:08,741
我没有地方可去。
I don't have nowhere to go.

1185
01:37:08,824 --> 01:37:11,744
是的，你需要。我需要一个厨师。
Yes, you do. I need a cook.

1186
01:37:13,245 --> 01:37:18,625
我已经厌倦了自己做的菜，我很想尝尝你提到的伯明翰鸡蛋。
I'm tired of my own cooking and I'm anxious to try those eggs Birmingham you mentioned.

1187
01:37:20,294 --> 01:37:21,962
成交了吗?
Is it a deal?

1188
01:37:23,714 --> 01:37:27,051
嗯…当然，一言为定，萝丝阿姨。
Well... Oh, sure, it's a deal, Aunt Rose.

1189
01:37:27,134 --> 01:37:29,970
