1342
01:50:41,177 --> 01:50:44,556
你能理解我的感受。不是吗，桑迪?
You understand how I feel. Don't you, Sandy?

1343
01:50:44,639 --> 01:50:52,105
请为…作为一个白人对另一个白人，就今晚，不要把他留在原地。
Please, as... as one white man to another, just for tonight, don't leave him on the place.

1344
01:50:52,188 --> 01:50:55,358
就今晚，桑迪。
Just tonight, Sandy.

1345
01:50:55,441 --> 01:50:57,694
哦。
Oh.

1346
01:50:57,777 --> 01:51:00,572
我的腿被那棵树皮划伤了。
I've scratched my leg on the bark of that tree.

1347
01:51:00,655 --> 01:51:02,490
瓦卡罗，过来。
Vacarro, come here.

1348
01:51:02,574 --> 01:51:04,367
原谅我。
Excuse me.

1349
01:51:06,661 --> 01:51:08,329
现在你在想什么?
Now what you got on your mind?

1350
01:51:08,413 --> 01:51:10,373
听着，伙计，我们一无所有
Listen, fella, we ain't got nothin'

1351
01:51:10,456 --> 01:51:12,000
留住那个老男孩。
to hold that old boy on.

1352
01:51:12,083 --> 01:51:16,129
他一直在院子里扫射，但他告诉我们有个坏蛋在抓他的鸡。
He's been shootin' up his yard a little, but he tells us a varmint's been catchin' his chickens.

1353
01:51:16,212 --> 01:51:21,718
他的鸡吗?我有一份重要证人签署的认罪书，相当于一份宣誓书。
His chickens? I've got a signed confession by a material witness that amounts to an affidavit.

1354
01:51:21,801 --> 01:51:23,696
除非有人目睹并拍照。
Not till it's witnessed by others and Photostated.

1355
01:51:23,720 --> 01:51:26,490
我们会找人见证并拍照…我不需要你的任何东西。
We'll have it witnessed and photographed... I don't need anything from you.

1356
01:51:26,514 --> 01:51:27,616
我不想要你的任何东西。
I don't want anything from you.

1357
01:51:27,640 --> 01:51:29,142
我要去找县警长。
I'm going to the county sheriff.

1358
01:51:29,225 --> 01:51:30,226
摇滚!
Rock!

1359
01:51:30,310 --> 01:51:32,645
在这里,席尔瓦。
Here, Silva.

1360
01:51:32,729 --> 01:51:35,064
这里!
Here!

1361
01:51:35,148 --> 01:51:37,775
但是，席尔瓦，那我呢?
But, hey, Silva, how about me?

1362
01:51:37,859 --> 01:51:39,277
现在?
Now?

1363
01:51:42,030 --> 01:51:44,574
我明天会带更多的棉花回来!
I'll be coming back tomorrow with lots more cotton!

1364
01:51:46,910 --> 01:51:49,245
我明天会带更多的棉花回来!
I'll be back tomorrow with lots more cotton!

1365
01:52:03,843 --> 01:52:06,512
-他走了。-现在怎么办?
- Well, he's gone. - What happens now?

1366
01:52:06,596 --> 01:52:10,558
他果然拿到了你妻子签字的认罪书。
Well, he sure enough got hisself a signed confession from your wife.

1367
01:52:10,642 --> 01:52:13,728
现在为了面子，我们得把这事过一遍。
Now we're gonna have to go through this thing for appearance's sake.

1368
01:52:13,811 --> 01:52:15,855
我不是那个意思。我的意思是……
I don't mean that. I mean...

1369
01:52:19,484 --> 01:52:22,403
明天会发生什么?
what happens tomorrow?

1370
01:52:22,487 --> 01:52:26,241
镇法警管不了明天的事。
Well, the town marshal has no control over tomorrow.

1371
01:52:49,097 --> 01:52:51,349
今天是我宝贝娃娃的生日。
Today is my Baby Doll's birthday.

1372
01:52:59,357 --> 01:53:01,693
你的朋友忘了我。
Your friend forgot me.

1373
01:53:04,529 --> 01:53:08,950
阿奇·李，看来庆祝结束了。
Well, Archie Lee, it looks like the celebration is over.

1374
01:53:09,033 --> 01:53:12,245
我们走吧。
Let's go.

1375
01:53:12,328 --> 01:53:15,415
他明天会带更多的棉花回来。
He's coming back tomorrow with more cotton.

1376
01:53:15,498 --> 01:53:17,625
他要回来了?
He's coming back?

1377
01:53:35,226 --> 01:53:38,813
哦，好吧，我们现在进去吧。
Oh, well, let's go in now.

1378
01:53:38,896 --> 01:53:51,534
我们无事可做，只能等到明天……看看我们会不会被记住……或被遗忘。
We got nothin' to do, but wait for tomorrow... and see if we are remembered... or forgotten.


